	}
}

{

		id
		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}

mutation ($payload:OAuthUpdateAccessTokenInput!)

		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)

	{

		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)

		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
